  Then Click on the Apply button
  Then Click on the Reset button
  When Click in the Supplier field and select a Supplier "<Supplier>"
  Then Click on the Apply button
  Then Click on the Reset button
  When Click in the Item Name field and select a Item Name "<Items>"
  Then Click on the Apply button
  Then Click on the Reset button
